description: We are the world's partner in parenting
title: What is BabyCenter
content:
Created by BabyCenter

Baby Center is a parenting website providing information on conception, pregnancy, birth, and early childhood for parents and parents-to-be.
The site has been online since November 1997.

Users of the website can sign up for free weekly email newsletters that guide them through pregnancy and their child's development.
